Class ConfigFormProvider

  • java.lang.Object
    • uk.ac.ed.epcc.webapp.AbstractContexed
      • uk.ac.ed.epcc.webapp.forms.registry.FormFactoryProviderRegistry
        • uk.ac.ed.epcc.webapp.model.data.forms.registry.ConfigFormProvider
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    UIGenerator, Contexed, TransitionFactoryCreator, NodeMaker

    public class ConfigFormProvider
extends FormFactoryProviderRegistry
    A FormProviderRegistry for DataObjectFactories that is configured via properties. Configuration properties are:
    • tag.tables Comma seperated list of table names to manage
    • tag.title Name of registry
    • class.table-name Class of table
    • tag.table-name.name Name to use for table (defaults to table-name).
    Update/create priviledge is given to users via the (Update|Create)(tag|table-name) role.
